 the plastic cups and incubated to 300-350C for about 2 to 4 hrs.\n\n BENEFITS & ADVANTAGES\nForced convection system ensures good mixing, strong dispersion and maintains higher temperature uniformity inside the chamber.\nSynthetic door gasket made of neoprene on the double walled door.\nUser oriented design of shelves makes you adjust each space of shelves without difficulty.\n CONSTRUCTIONAL FEATURES\nOuter body made up of PCGI steel sheet duly powder coated. Inner chamber and perforated trays made of stainless steel (SS-304).\nSpace between inner chamber and outer wall is filled with high grade insulation for minimal heat dissipation.\n\n Bigger sized units mounted on caster wheels for easy portability.\n\n Door fitted with heavy duty hinges and door handle ensuring there are no leakages through the door gasket.\nSynthetic door gasket made of neoprene rubber is fitted to all KIRAN units instead of asbestos. \nTo work on 220/230V AV, 50/60 Hz supply','2021-03-02 01:19:45','Active'),(4,'Ss Yogurt Incubator, Capacity: 500 Litres/Hr',1,1,'1.44 Lakh','122333','Product Specification\nCapacity	500 litres/hr\nEquipment Type	YOGURT INCUBATOR\nMaterial	SS\nAutomation Grade	Automatic\nPhase	Single\nVoltage	220 / 440\nBrand	KIRAN\nMinimum Order Quantity	1 Piece\nProduct Description\nProduct Description\n\nYOGURT INCUBATOR are one of the finest quality milk processing equipment used prominently is food processing & dairy industries.\n\n \n\nIt is milk processing equipment used for speeding up the bacterial fermentation process if the milk which results in yogurt or dahi. Yogurt is further processed to make many other products like Ghee, shrikhand etc.\n\n \n\nDahi incubator/Yogurt Incubator a milk processing equipment that follows a simple process for making dahi or yogurt wherein the milk is boiled and then cooled to the room temperature. This cooled milk is then mixed with bacterial culture which is used for the milk fermentation. After the thorough mixing of the milk it is then filled in the plastic cups and incubated to 300-350C for about 2 to 4 hrs.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nBENEFITS & ADVANTAGES\n\n \n\nForced convection system ensures good mixing, strong dispersion and maintains higher temperature uniformity inside the chamber.\n\n \n\nSynthetic door gasket made of neoprene on the double walled door.\n\n \n\nUser oriented design of shelves makes you adjust each space of shelves without difficulty.\n\n \n\n CONSTRUCTIONAL FEATURES\n\n \n\nOuter body made up of PCGI steel sheet duly powder coated. Inner chamber and perforated trays made of stainless steel (SS-304).\n\n \n\nSpace between inner chamber and outer wall is filled with high grade insulation for minimal heat dissipation.\n\n \n\nBigger sized units mounted on caster wheels for easy portability.\n\n \n\nDoor fitted with heavy duty hinges and door handle ensuring there are no leakages through the door gasket.\n\n \n\nSynthetic door gasket made of neoprene rubber is fitted to all KIRAN units instead of asbestos.\n\n \n\nTo work on 220/230V AV, 50/60 Hz supply','2021-03-02 01:20:58','Active'),(5,'Automatic Mild Steel Bread Slicer',2,1,'40000','122333','Product Specification\nOperation Mode	Automatic\nMachine Body Material	Mild Steel\nCapacity	1000 Pieces/day\nMotor Power	0.5 HP\nPhase Type	Single Phase\nVoltage	230V\nBrand	DS\nProduct Description\nBacked by years of industry experience, we are engaged in offering a premium quality range of Mild Steel Bread Slicer.','2021-03-02 01:23:57','Active'),(6,'Sewing Machines',3,1,'50000','1111','The Sewing Machines CN-4 model (Citizen 95 T-10) is designed on the lines of the sewing machines CN-3 with an additional advantage of a slick square arm for grace & beauty. It is widely appreciated for reverse and straight stitching and auto trip bobbin winder-functions. The sewing machine is rewind thread automatically and comes with drawer and double thread for accelerating its speed. It can sew sleeves and easily adjust stitch width for perfect stit